<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EMA514_04_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css">
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="../../common_contents/js/ema514_04_0003.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema514_04.css">

</head>
<body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_04_su_0003">
        <section class="title type2">
            <h2 data-head="1" lang="y" class="fraction_box_title">
                <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                  <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                    준서는 바비큐 한 개를 <span class="fraction_box"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>만큼 먹었습니다. 준서가 먹은 바비큐의 양을 간단한 분수로 나타내는 방법을 알아봅시다.
                  </div>
                </div>
            </h2>
        </section>

        <section class="contents paging_layout">
            
            <div class="input_area">
                 <article class="page page_1">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                          <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                            <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>과 같은 크기만큼 색칠하고, 분수로 나타내어 보세요.
                          </div>
                        </div>                        
                    </h3>
                    <div class="question_box justify_center">
                        <div class="count_wrap">
                            <div class="count_row">
                                <span class="num">0</span>
                                <span class="num num1">1</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box f32b" lang="y"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="count_row">                                
                                <span class="num">0</span>
                                <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="4">
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                </div>
                                <span class="num num1">1</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="(4)/(8)"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="count_row">
                                <span class="num">0</span>
                                <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="2">
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                </div>
                                <span class="num num1">1</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(4)"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="count_row">
                                <span class="num">0</span>
                                <div class="boolean_count_wrap" data-answer-single="1">
                                    <button></button>
                                    <button></button>
                                </div>
                                <span class="num num1">1</span>
                                <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap" data-hint-position="right">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="(1)/(2)"></math-field>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="page page_2">
                    <h3 lang="y">
                        분모와 분자를 각각 0이 아닌 같은 수로 나누어 간단한 분수로 나타내어 보세요.
                    </h3>
                    <div class="question_box justify_center">
                        <div class="fraction_col col1">
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8 &divide; 2</span><span>16 &divide; 2</span></div>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b">
                                <div class="input_wrap f32b">
                                    <math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field>
                                </div>
                                <span>8</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fraction_col col2">
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b">
                                <span>
                                    8&divide;
                                    <span class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="4"></math-field></span>
                                </span>
                                <span>16&divide;4</span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(4)"></math-field>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fraction_col col3">
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <div class="fraction_box f32b">
                                <span>
                                    8&divide;
                                    <span class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="8"></math-field></span>
                                </span>
                                <span>16&divide;8</span>
                            </div>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                                <math-field data-answer-single="(1)/(2)"></math-field>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
            <article class="page page_3">
                <h3 lang="y">
                    <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                        <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                        <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>의 분모와 분자를 공통으로 나눈 수들은 어떤 특징이 있나요?
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </h3>
                <div>
                <div class="input_wrap">
                    <math-field class="textarea"></math-field>
                    <div class="example_box">
                        <p lang="y">분모 16과 분자 8의 공약수입니다.</p>
                        
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_4">
                <h3 lang="y">
                    <div class="fraction_txt_wrap">
                        <div class="fraction_txt" lang="y">
                            <span class="fraction_box ml_0"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>을 간단히 나타낸 분수 중에서 분모와 분자의 공약수가 1뿐인 분수를 찾아보세요.
                        </div>
                    </div>                    
                </h3>
                <div class="question_box justify_center">
                    <div class="fraction_col">
                        <div class="fraction_inn">
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8 &divide; 2</span><span>16 &divide; 2</span></span>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>4</span><span>8</span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fraction_inn">
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8 &divide; 4</span><span>16 &divide; 4</span></span>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>2</span><span>4</span></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="fraction_inn">
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8</span><span>16</span></span>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>8 &divide; 8</span><span>16 &divide; 8</span></span>
                            <span class="f32b">=</span>
                            <span class="fraction_box f32b"><span>1</span><span>2</span></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fraction_col">
                        <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                            <math-field data-answer-single="(1)/(2)"></math-field>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            <article class="page page_5">
                <div class="summarize_wrap">
                    <div class="summarize">
                        <label lang="y">정리해 볼까요</label>
                        <div>
                            <span lang="y">분모와 분자를 1이 아닌 공약수로 나누어 간단한 분수로 나타내는 것을</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <button class="reveal_btn revel_act" data-pair="1">약분</button>
                            <span lang="y" class="small-gap">한다고 합니다.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="summarize_row row2">
                            <div class="sum_col">
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>8&divide;2</span><span>16&divide;2</span></div>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>8</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sum_col">
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>8&divide;4</span><span>16&divide;4</span></div>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>2</span><span>4</span></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="sum_col">
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>8</span><span>16</span></div>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>8&divide;8</span><span>16&divide;8</span></div>
                                <span>=</span>
                                <div class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span lang="y">이때 <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></span>과 같이 분모와 분자의 공약수가 1뿐인 분수를 </span>
                            <button class="reveal_btn" data-pair="1">기약분수</button>
                            <span lang="y" class="small-gap">라고 합니다.</span>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="speech_bubble">
                            <div class="bubble_txt">
                                <div class="bubble_row b_row1" lang="y">
                                    약분은 
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span class="num1">8</span><span class="num2">16</span><i class="num3">1</i><i class="num4">2</i></span>
                                    <span>=</span>
                                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>2</span></span>
                                    과 같이 
                                </div>
                                <div class="bubble_row b_row2" lang="y">
                                    나타낼 수도 있어요.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </article>
            
            <div class="btn_area">
                <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
                <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
                <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
                <button class="btnSubmit">확인</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>